 He was like, "You? Teaching on forgiveness? Seriously?"

16
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:07,480
 And yeah, why did he laugh?

17
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:10,360
 Something that he has been teasing me a lot is,

18
