 So it's helpful for me at work because I remember things,

22
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:30,000
 gets me more efficient, and also for me to be in a bigger church community,

23
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:32,520
 it helps me to remember people as well.

24
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:38,360
 But it's really unhelpful when we talk about forgiveness.

25
