00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:12,400
 Because when I was growing up, there was a lot of emotional abuse.

467
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:15,040
 So I would withdraw.

468
00:35:15,040 --> 00:35:21,360
 I would try to stay away from the pain, the source of the pain.

469
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:24,480
 And I will grow up to become a very self-reliant person

