00:35:24,480 --> 00:35:27,200
 because I want to minimize my reliance on people

471
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:30,320
 so that I will have less pain, right?

472
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:33,440
 Basically, that's how I coped with it when I was growing up.

473
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:36,560
 When I grew up, when I was in my late 20s,

474
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:40,400
 so I learned a very valuable lesson in church life,

